{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/newsupdates_firefoxsend/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"271a7c3e-807c-5538-8970-682c5d7f0505","html":"<p><img src=\"/media/firefoxsend_cover.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"firefox-send-是什麼\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#firefox-send-%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC\" aria-label=\"firefox send 是什麼 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Firefox Send 是什麼?</h2>\n<p>在 <a href=\"/posts/ep7-computer-habits-that-shouldnt-be-contempted#%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6--%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%E7%A2%9F-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85\">上一集</a> 和大家推薦的<a href=\"https://send.firefox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"> Firefox Send</a> 是由 Mozilla (Firefox 的開發商) 所開發的線上傳檔工具，上傳時檔案會被自動加密存放於伺服器上，並產生能設定下載後失效的連結。</p>\n<h2 id=\"事發\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BC\" aria-label=\"事發 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>事發</h2>\n<p>有心人士利用 Firefox Send 散播惡意程式，包含幾個有名的惡意組織 FIN7, REVil (Sodinokibi), Ursnif (Dreambot), 和 Zloader。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/firefoxsend_twitter_zdnet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>圖片來源：<a href=\"https://www.zdnet.com/article/mozilla-suspends-firefox-send-service-while-it-addresses-malware-abuse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ZDNet - Mozilla suspends Firefox Send service while it addresses malware abuse</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"為什麼是-firefox-send\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%98%AF-firefox-send\" aria-label=\"為什麼是 firefox send permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>為什麼是 Firefox Send</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>可以簡單快速生成可信度較高的網址</li>\n<li>不易在雲端留下資料</li>\n<li>提高 IP 位址被追蹤的難度</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"目前情況\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81\" aria-label=\"目前情況 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>目前情況</h2>\n<p>Mozilla 將 Firefox Send 下架，目前正在針對濫用情況進行調查</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/firefoxsend_suspend.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"未來規劃\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83\" aria-label=\"未來規劃 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>未來規劃</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“We will temporarily take Firefox Send offline while we make improvements to the product. Before relaunching, we will be adding an abuse reporting mechanism to augment the existing Feedback form, and we will require all users wishing to share content using Firefox Send to sign in with a Firefox Account.” - Mozilla’s response to ZDNet</p>\n<p>(翻譯) “在我們將 Firefox Send 改善的同時，我們會將 Firefox Send 暫時下架。再重新上架前，我們將會新增濫用回報機制，並要求用戶登入 Firefox 帳號來使用 Firefox Send。” - Mozilla 對 ZDNet (美國科技新聞網)採訪的回應</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"替代方案\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" aria-label=\"替代方案 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>替代方案</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.myairbridge.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">MyAirBridge</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>可透過 Email / 連結分享檔案</li>\n<li>免費板自動於檔案上傳後三天刪除</li>\n<li>無法設定密碼</li>\n<li>最大可傳輸檔案大小為 20G</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://fromsmash.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Smash</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>可購過 Email / 連結 / Slack 分享檔案</li>\n<li>可設定密碼保護/時間限制</li>\n<li>無檔案大小限制</li>\n<li>需輸入 Email (可提供假 Email)</li>\n<li>可同時分享多個檔案。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"資料新聞來源\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90\" aria-label=\"資料新聞來源 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>資料/新聞來源</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.zdnet.com/article/mozilla-suspends-firefox-send-service-while-it-addresses-malware-abuse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ZDNet - Mozilla suspends Firefox Send service while it addresses malware abuse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nakedsecurity.sophos.com/2020/07/08/mozilla-turns-off-firefox-send-following-malware-abuse-reports/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Mozilla turns off “Firefox Send” following malware abuse reports</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2020-07-09-news-updates-firefox-send-暫時下架了//posts/newsupdates_firefoxsend","tagSlugs":["/tag/firefox-send/","/tag/mozilla/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-07-08T14:05:43.914Z","description":"在上一集提供給大家這個可以在不同裝置間更方便傳送檔案的工具，在昨天下架了！","tags":["Firefox Send","Mozilla"],"title":"Firefox Send 暫時下架了","socialImage":"/media/firefoxsend_cover.png"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2020-07-09-news-updates-firefox-send-暫時下架了//posts/newsupdates_firefoxsend"}},"static